abstract: Ligaya Mishan reviews Goa Taco restaurant on Lower East Side.
lead_paragraph: In lieu of tortillas, the fillings at this “semi-permanent” spot are served inside paratha, a many-layered Indian flatbread.

headline.main: Goa Taco Takes Liberties on the Lower East Side
headline.print_headline: Taking a Few Liberties With Tacos
